divs: Sighting DetailsI went outside to lock my car in the driveway, afterward I went to the backyard to look at the stars. I was looking up to he northwest and two white star like objects caught my eye. They were in a staggered flight path going from the northwest to the south. At first I thought that these might have been planes at high altitude or satellites but as they were flying the trailing object made what I guess I would call circular movements near the object in front and then both accelerated and eventually disappeared
